<div class="mb-5">
  <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">
    About Dog Breed Explorer
  </h1>

  <p class="lead">
    This Ruby on Rails application displays dog breeds,
    sub-breeds, and dog images.
  </p>
</div>

<section class="mb-5">
  <h2>Project Description</h2>

  <p>
    Dog Breed Explorer is a Ruby on Rails project that uses
    information collected from the Dog CEO API. Users can browse
    dog breeds, search by breed name, filter results, view
    sub-breeds, and view dog images.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="mb-5">
  <h2>Data Sources</h2>

  <p>
    The main data source is the Dog CEO API. It is a public API
    that returns data in JSON format. The application uses the API
    to collect breed names, sub-breed names, and dog image URLs.
  </p>

  <p>
    Faker is also used to generate simple breed descriptions.
    The names and images are not generated by Faker.
  </p>

  <h3 class="h5">API endpoints</h3>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <code>https://dog.ceo/api/breeds/list/all</code>
    </li>

    <li>
      <code>https://dog.ceo/api/breed/{breed}/images/random/3</code>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="mb-5">
  <h2>Database Structure</h2>

  <p>
    The application contains three main database tables:
    breeds, sub_breeds, and dog_images.
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>
      One breed can have many sub-breeds.
    </li>

    <li>
      Each sub-breed belongs to one breed.
    </li>

    <li>
      One breed can have many dog images.
    </li>

    <li>
      Each dog image belongs to one breed.
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="mb-5">
  <h2>Database ERD</h2>

  <figure class="text-center">
    <%= image_tag "dog_breed_erd.png",
                  alt: "ERD showing the breeds, sub-breeds, and dog images tables",
                  class: "img-fluid border rounded shadow-sm erd-image" %>

    <figcaption class="text-muted mt-2">
      Dog Breed Explorer database relationship diagram.
    </figcaption>
  </figure>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Application Features</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Breed collection page</li>
    <li>Breed detail pages</li>
    <li>Sub-breed detail pages</li>
    <li>Dog image detail pages</li>
    <li>Breed name search</li>
    <li>Sub-breed filtering</li>
    <li>Featured breed filtering</li>
    <li>Pagination</li>
  </ul>
</section>